I am converting our robot from labview to java. I am trying to create a doublesolenoid, but I just keep getting ‘CAN: message not found’ errors. I know the wiring is fine because it all works with labview. I am using the same ports they are using with labview. They are plugged into a rev robotics pnuematics hub. The hub is tied into the CAN. I tried creating a pnuematichub, but that also throws the same not found message. What am I missing here?

solenoid = new DoubleSolenoid(
PneumaticsModuleType.REVPH,
PnuematicChannels.ALGAE_GRABBER_FORWARD,
PnuematicChannels.ALGAE_GRABBER_REVERSE);
